data.description: Beautiful top floor condo, close to downtown, freeways and shopping. Awesome family room with elegant bamboo floor and lots of room.   Cute kitchen with spacious counter, lots of storage and more. Bathroom is clean and in great shape.  Bedroom has great view of the pool and large closet.  Covered parking spot for your vehicle and other parking available.  Security with gated parking and locked condo building.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from tax ID.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
